# Product Model

> The Domain Model of DailyPaws

This document describes the core concepts that exist in DailyPaws.

It is technology independent.

It explains what the product knows, not how it is implemented.

---

# Core Principles

The Product Model describes concepts.

Not screens.

Not databases.

Not APIs.

Every concept should answer four questions:

- Why does it exist?
- What does DailyPaws know?
- How does it evolve?
- Which other concepts does it relate to?

